title: Dr. Oz Makes Final Bid to Connect With Pennsylvania Voters
description: For years, Dr. Oz engaged millions of Americans as a television celebrity. Now his task is to connect with Pennsylvanians as a candidate.
dc:creator: Katie Glueck
media:credit: Hilary Swift for The New York Times
media:description: Dr. Mehmet Oz addressed a barn full of voters in Elizabethtown, Pa., on Wednesday, a rare large-scale public rally.
